      "text": [
        "359 - وَقَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «إِنَّ بَيْنَ اَلدُّنْيَا وَ اَلْآخِرَةِ أَلْفَ عَقَبَةٍ أَهْوَنُهَا وَ أَيْسَرُهَا اَلْمَوْتُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.359 - The Imam (as) said:\n\"Indeed, between this world and the Hereafter, there are a thousand obstacles, the easiest and least difficult of which is death.\""
        ]
      }
    }
